snippet.title: Midnight Blood Rush | ✨ NEW ✨ Demo Release Trailer 🩸
snippet.description:
Our new demo is finally released on Steam!

Wishlist the game on Steam and play the demo here 👉 https://store.steampowered.com/app/2502310/Midnight_Blood_Rush/

"Midnight Blood Rush" is a dazzling vampiric roguelite, in which you pay for upgrades with your health points, and recover some every time you devour an enemy!

You can also test our other games here 👉 https://guilloteam.itch.io/

Join us!
Discord | https://discord.gg/AcQM2Awr
Twitter | https://twitter.com/TeamGuillo
TikTok | https://www.tiktok.com/@teamguillo

Original Soundtrack 🎵 | By Delphin Casado 🎹
